Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena... aku ingin sekali\Npergi jalan-jalan bersamamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Berjuanglah, Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, sekalian aja mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin tidak sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan waktu yang tepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri aku waktu sebentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kami mengajak Sakuma\Ndan Kusunoki ke pantai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kali pertamaku\Nke pantai bersama teman-teman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak terlalu suka air asin,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku akan baik-baik saja\Ndengan persiapan dan simulasi mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, aku sangat menantikannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rencana ke pantai kami akhirnya\Nmelibatkan anak Kelas 2-A lainnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baju renang siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Handuk siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tabir surya sudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tatsuta, sampaikan salam Ibu pada Yohei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berangkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah hari perjalanan pantai\Nyang sangat kami tunggu-tunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka punya paket pantai khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lucu sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita di pantai! Pantai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita masih di stasiun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat kau tidak kesiangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku tidak tidur...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergi ke pantai bersama mereka\Nmembuatku gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Otori juga merasa gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo! Kita pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan cepat-cepat! Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa pakai baju renang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung aku berusaha keras agar bisa datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergi sana, iblis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kalian coba menyentuhnya,\Nrasakan akibatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelah sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Luna!\N- Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Air mengalir dan garam,\Nserangan ganda antivampir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak apa-apa, Luna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku... tidak... menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung dia tidak tersapu ke laut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa, mana topimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan selamatkan topi Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perlombaan dimulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang akan memenangkan Derbi Topi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia selalu yang tercepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuna Sirip Biru dari Kashinokidai, Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawannya adalah pendatang baru,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Komedi Lautan, Deguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Persaingan kedua atlet ini sangat sengit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita dengar pendapat\Nkomentator kita, Hashimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mendadak sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang mereka lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sepersekian detik lebih cepat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong kosong, aku satu milimeter\Nlebih dulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!\NKita mau main apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagian besar pilihan kita\Nmelibatkan masuk ke air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau voli pantai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah jauh-jauh ke pantai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin masuk ke air...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin gabung dengan yang lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan atasi kelemahanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini cukup dangkal, kau bisa berdiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah buru-buru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sentuh aku sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat bulu kuduknya berdiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakiku kena...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Luna!\N- Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Kok bisa tenggelam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia menyusut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi kau muat di ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Otori dari tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa... kau...\NAku akan selamatkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tenggelam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal areanya dangkal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku juga tak bisa berenang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kalian ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan memaksakan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kurasa aku hampir\Nmengatasi rasa takutku pada air!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat kalian berdua!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian cuma perlu menggendongku\Nsaat di air!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakinya belum menyentuh air!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang lapar?\NAku sudah buat makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat makan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makannya banyak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bicara sambil makan!\NNanti tersedak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minum air, kunyah 100 kali,\Njangan makan berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih muat banyak, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa, mereka punya kakigori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakigori! Aku belum pernah coba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?! Ayo pesan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantiknya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanlah sebelum meleleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dingin dan enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Warnanya biru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini penyakit mematikan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada dokter di sini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Seseorang! Siapa pun!\N- Itu cuma kakigori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau makan banyak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keponakanku pandai mengurus anak-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pamannya Otori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paman! Terima kasih sudah menerima kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanannya enak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang kau menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tidak bertemu, Tacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu kau sering bawa teman-temanmu ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman-Teman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang mau membangun istana pasir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Istana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedengarannya seru! Aku ikut!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekali lagi terima kasih, Paman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menikmati makanannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanannya enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Otori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, ingin rasanya jadi muda kembali...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bakal jadi istana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo buat yang besar!\NSebesar Gunung Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba jadi ekstrem banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mimpi harus besar, tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus bergabung!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Gali sungai di sini!\N- Belum pernah main ini sejak TK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kejutkan mereka\Ndengan hasil karya kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gimana? Gimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kami pemenangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Ishikawa tersenyum pada kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin lihat senyumnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, pasirnya masuk mulutku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terus mencuri perhatian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya mereka bocah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matahari terbenamnya syahdu sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti rasanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa mereka kompak sekali soal itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!\NAyo berenang menuju matahari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak boleh berenang!\NSebentar lagi gelap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, aduh, aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok bisa, Bos?!\NKan ada aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicara apa kau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!\NAyo berlomba di pantai saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan jadi wasit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lelah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya mengagumi cantiknya\Npemandangan langit dan laut dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar!\NIni posisi terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun bisa melihat ini dari pantai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi yang terbaik itu\Nsaat melihatnya bersama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Kau benar sekali, Eiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat bersenang-senang...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Luna! Apa selanjutnya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau semangat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat apa yang kupunya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kembang api!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga bawa ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jenis yang ditembakkan ke langit!\NKeren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiap cowok mendambakan\Nkembang api besar yang meledak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mundur setidaknya lima meter\Nsetelah dinyalakan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan melongok ke dalam tabung\Njika api padam di tengah jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimengerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kufoto, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya kembang api.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini untukmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yui, pinjam apimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa, mau nyalakan punyamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantiknya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan? Sangat cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakuma! Kusunoki!\NMau nyalakan kembang api kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menirunya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat, sebelum padam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ya.\N- Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kufoto, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dilambaikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah padam...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat, masukkan ke air untuk berjaga-jaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih ada lagi.\NAda yang aneh juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa benar-benar\Ntidak terlihat di foto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang bilang mereka tak bisa\Nmemotretnya untuk wawancara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau bagaimana lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan kutukanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau ini jadi penggantiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembang bola api!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begini lebih mirip andaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang lain selain bola api.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, ini, dan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga rekomendasikan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Aku ingin coba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang kau pikirkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, cuma merenung.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kapan terakhir kali\Naku main kembang api.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sering memainkannya\Nwaktu pertama kali pindah ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah padam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagiku, sebelumnya semua ini\Ncuma hal yang kubaca di manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya hari ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, aku mulai dapat ide\Napa yang harus digambar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak lupa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bagaimana?\NSudah dapat subjeknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi... coba kupikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah cukup lama aku tidak main\Natau bergaul dalam kelompok besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sangat menikmatinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat bersenang-senang\Nsampai lupa kalau lapar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa, bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}rasanya aku telah membuat\Nkenangan musim panas berharga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal liburan musim panas belum mulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa melakukan apa pun jika berusaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana karyamu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu di sana, 'kan?!\NTunjukkan padaku! Tunjukkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, aku akan lihat\Nsetelah kau kumpulkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah! Ayolah! Ayolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak menggambar apa pun kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak... menggambar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Maksudku,\Nini bukan untuk dikumpulkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalahnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menggambar... ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf tidak bertanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu kau tak muncul di foto, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada masalah dengan foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:20:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Foto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak terlihat di foto karena aku vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memikirkannya sejak saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir kau butuh sesuatu\Nuntuk mengingat hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku ingin kau memiliki lukisan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku tidak mungkin\Nikut kompetisi dengan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf! Maaf! Maaf!\NKau tak apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih banyak tempat lain\Nyang ingin aku kunjungi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat tempat yang kutandai ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bintangnya indah sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat ini juga bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, yang ini wajib!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita jalan-jalan lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau ikut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pendengaranmu tajam sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya\Ndi Li'l Miss Vampire Can't Suck Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Nona Vampir Kecil\Ndan Dimulainya Liburan Musim Panas".
